{"tid":1721200,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"守住春袋，定棄守?","createTime":"2019-11-14T15:02:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T15:08:11.000Z","uid":286550,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2b66ee34af279d930b850c19f419b4b39c7b9a75","tid":1721200,"uid":286550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:02:22.000Z","msg":"On9仔自話自說:<br />\n<br />\n我地優勢Be water. <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一沾即走做到效果而不戀戰。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />對方無針可施，變左亂9拉人。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Keep住打國際戰線，網絡戰線。<br />\n<br />\n到已家，感覺有啲似俾人迫到一個地方。在俾大家守住左城堡，好似嬴左場杖。俾左大家好似有個希望，另到大家更團結。但係呢個地方亦成為左我地既春袋。<br />\n若然佢一舉包圍，無論Cu,或Pu等將會無兄弟走得甩。<br />\n<br />\n所以佢要散走內地生，同埋可能假意俾你Win場。令大家聚埋一齊。好可能係將我地既Be water，搵左個地方聚埋。在一舉攻破。"},{"pid":"8c8a2dc7a58aa137e02f2dff89f3199d7096f770","tid":1721200,"uid":190793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:03:06.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n［韓國戰線］青瓦台請願聯署 同我簽爆佢 （教學）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1720736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1720736</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0b1ebfbd41cd76fffcccf0f4f8e95c9176ba12f1","tid":1721200,"uid":259613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:08:00.000Z","msg":"keep全大三罷"},{"pid":"530abe273e4db82b40b50ebe42635d69d06312b3","tid":1721200,"uid":259613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b1ebfbd41cd76fffcccf0f4f8e95c9176ba12f1","tid":1721200,"uid":259613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:08:00.000Z","msg":"keep全大三罷"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:08:11.000Z","msg":"住"}]}